passages.name: Additional Coverage
passages.text:
<Message>
  Choose Additional Coverage!
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="[isTravel,isAccident]"
          value="[true,false]"
  >
    [[Travel->Start]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="[isTravel,isAccident]"
          value="[false,true]"
  >
    [[Accident->Start]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="[isTravel,isAccident]"
          value="[true,true]"
  >
    [[Both->Start]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="[isTravel,isAccident]"
          value="[false,false]"
  >
    [[None->Start]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: prevInsurerTravelCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[travelInsurer]]"
          when="isTravel == true"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[prevInsurerAccidentCheck]]"
          when="isAccident == true"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[youthEligibilityCheck]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: youthEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[email]]"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || livingSpace > 50 || coInsured > 0"
          key="isYouth"
          value="false"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[youth]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: accidentEnabled
passages.text:
<Message>
  Is accident enable?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="isAccidentEnabled"
          value="true"
  >
    [[Yes->Main Coverage]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="isAccidentEnabled"
          value="false"
  >
    [[No->Main Coverage]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: name
passages.text:
<Message>
  {NO_SIGNUP_NAME_MESSAGE_FIRST}
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[{EMBARK_CONTINUE}->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="{FIRST_NAME}"
              placeholder="{EMBARK_NAME_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{EMBARK_SURNAME}"
              placeholder="{EMBARK_LAST_NAME_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: address
passages.text:
<Message>
  {NO_SIGNUP_ADDRESS_MESSAGE}
</Message>

<Response>
  {street}, {zipCode}
</Response>

<TextActionSet next="[[{EMBARK_CONTINUE}->sizeInput]]">
  <TextAction title="{NO_SIGNUP_ADDRESS_LABEL}"
              placeholder="{NO_SIGNUP_ADDRESS_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="street"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{NO_SIGNUP_POSTAL_CODE}"
              mask="NorwegianPostalCode"
              placeholder="{NO_SIGNUP_POSTAL_CODE_PLACEHOLDER}"
              key="zipCode"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: Main Coverage
passages.text:
<Message>
  Choose Main Coverage!
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="[isHomeContents,isHouse]"
          value="[true,false]"
  >
    [[Home Contents->Additional Coverage]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="[isHomeContents,isHouse]"
          value="[false,true]"
  >
    [[House->Additional Coverage]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="[isHomeContents,isHouse]"
          value="[true,true]"
  >
    [[Both->Additional Coverage]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: householdSize
passages.text:
<Message>
  {NO_SIGNUP_HOUSEHOLD_SIZE_MESSAGE}
</Message>

<Response>
  <when expression="householdSize > 1">
    {householdSize} {EMBARK_HOUSEHOLD_UNIT}
  </when>
  <when expression="householdSize == 1">
    {EMBARK_JUST_ME}
  </when>
</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="2"
              minvalue="1"
              key="householdSize"
              next="[[{EMBARK_CONTINUE}->isHouseholdSizeValid]]"
              unit="{EMBARK_HOUSEHOLD_UNIT}"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      {NO_SIGNUP_HOUSEHOLD_SIZE}
    </Title>
    <Description>
      {NO_SIGNUP_CO_INSURED_DESCRIPTION}
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</NumberAction>

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<Message>
  {EMBARK_OFFER_READY_MESSAGE}
</Message>

<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateNorwegianEnglishContentQuoteBundle(
	  $quoteCartId: ID!
	  $input: CreateQuoteBundleInput!
	) {
	  quoteCart_createQuoteBundle(id: $quoteCartId, input: $input) {
	  	__typename
		... on QuoteCart {
		  id
		}
		... on QuoteBundleError {
		  limits {
			code
		  }
		}
	  }
	}
  </Mutation>
  <Variable key="quoteCartId"
            from="quoteCartId"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].currentInsurer"
            from="currentInsurerContents"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <ConstantVariable key="input.payload[0].data.type"
                    value="NORWEGIAN_HOME_CONTENT"
                    as="string"
  >
  </ConstantVariable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.numberCoInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.livingSpace"
            from="livingSpace"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.street"
            from="street"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.zipCode"
            from="zipCode"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.subType"
            from="type"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.isYouth"
            from="isYouth"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[0].data.dataCollectionId"
            from="currentInsurerContents_dataCollectionId"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].currentInsurer"
            from="currentInsurerTravel"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <ConstantVariable key="input.payload[1].data.type"
                    value="NORWEGIAN_TRAVEL"
                    as="string"
  >
  </ConstantVariable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].data.numberCoInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].data.isYouth"
            from="isYouth"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="input.payload[1].data.dataCollectionId"
            from="currentInsurerTravel_dataCollectionId"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Error next="[[CreateQuoteError]]">
  </Error>
  <Result key="quoteCart_createQuoteBundle.__typename"
          as="createQuoteBundleResultTypename"
  >
  </Result>
</GraphQLApi>
